#content","cachedResultName":"#content"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[3861,1420],"id":"7b458b64-c800-456d-8faa-b0cc5a48ae6c","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Weekly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — weekly. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Read Recent from Notion","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"b6dd5c1a-9d10-6eb2-e608-094258ac2824","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Read Recent from Notion\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Newest First · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"8a41b8e3-89b7-ddc0-67ae-e608c305a195","name":"Note: Read Recent from Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Trim to Digest Size","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"68620096-7b33-5d17-665f-9359e663b825","name":"Note: Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Trim to Digest Size\n\nCaps the stream at 15 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Summarize Content (AI)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"4ab7e107-8c41-5402-8baf-d132d04347ab","name":"Note: Trim to Digest Size"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Content (AI)\n\nMap-reduce summarization chain — handles long content without blowing the context window.\n\nPorts: ①→ Render as HTML · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"09ffd5ee-bc19-a53c-234a-01909fbe2e8c","name":"Note: Summarize Content (AI)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Anthropic Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Summarize Content (AI)** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Anthropic API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,1090],"id":"c2ce4e68-e03e-7fb3-686e-afa574d03bf7","name":"Note: Anthropic Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Render as HTML\n\nConverts markdown to HTML for rich rendering in email/CMS.\n\nNext: Post Digest to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,520],"id":"00791b13-73b0-f0e1-d4c0-07c257556b7c","name":"Note: Render as HTML"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Post Digest to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Archive Digest in Notion · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,520],"id":"9cef887a-d94e-feb0-8953-11ec691b7d04","name":"Note: Post Digest to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Digest in Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Processing Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2181,520],"id":"c9bd7a47-e343-60e3-db4f-1c5b66311902","name":"Note: Archive Digest in Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty topic","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2505,520],"id":"2c9eb98c-4fed-d6e2-cf7a-a54c18dc7b9a","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty topic\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2829,520],"id":"9dd735b8-3996-b633-7374-2c0e344dd1e5","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty topic"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3153,520],"id":"298f0cba-ac60-826b-8134-aad4469cb304","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,520],"id":"1daa4696-3b90-95b4-9d91-edf5202285d5","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"48eec8ef-ae48-e49e-985c-b1308d29b001","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"49fe1930-cda1-2bda-f5ac-37fdc5dc9691","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,1540],"id":"62e12d46-eb2d-0fc6-72f3-1c7810c3ff92","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,1540],"id":"be874dc2-07f4-b1c1-db9e-b3ae26616138","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Draft social posts with Notion and WordPress with instant alerts\n\n**Pattern:** Content Generation · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nDraft social posts with Notion and WordPress with instant alerts. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual blog posts is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Read Recent from Notion → Newest First → Trim to Digest Size → Summarize Content (AI) → Render as HTML → Post Digest to Slack → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to content generation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating blog posts in content creation\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Improves response time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Anthropic API key; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"4c206e32-bcc4-9c78-c322-7e17d4f55192","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"040a1e1a-f126-90eb-3839-65e67facb60a","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"347e2716-6de6-a541-5b74-588ff6d9ae6f","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your blog posts process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"8d30d4bd-46ab-324d-a575-7e346d4e6172","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Read Recent from Notion","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Read Recent from Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Newest First","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Trim to Digest Size","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Trim to Digest Size":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Anthropic Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Summarize Content (AI)":{"main":[[{"node":"Render as HTML","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Render as HTML":{"main":[[{"node":"Post Digest to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Post Digest to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Digest in Notion","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Digest in Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty topic","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty topic":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"53efc0a0-797e-47e4-a5d7-7f4ea4257c4a","id":"FDX05232"}